OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1993FBBC News introduced a new
OL,7,Fvirtual studio for use by domestic news
OL,8,Fprogrammes, on BBC One and BBC Two.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe opening sequence wide shot featured
OL,11,Fan impressive studio set - much of
OL,12,Fwhich was computer-generated (with the
OL,13,Fexception of a portion of the desk and
OL,14,Fthe backdrop behind the presenters).
OL,15,
OL,16,FDaytime bulletins, weekend
OL,17,Fdaytime/evening programmes, the One
OL,18,Fo'Clock News and the Six o'Clock News
OL,19,Fall had a similar appearance (albeit
OL,20,Fdifferent theme tunes).
OL,21,
OL,22,FThe Nine o'Clock News and Breakfast
